lead_paragraph: Formula One, fast cars and fizz make an alluring combination at the Monaco Grand Prix but the drawn-out shout of 'Champaaaagne' will be absent when the corks pop on the podium after this year's race.

headline.print_headline: Champagne Silence on Sparkling Monaco Podium
